Condor:

"Uhmmm" thought Condor while he continued shotting and avoiding the 
shots "It's time to run..."

He increased the speed and started to left the place, when some of 
the shot hit him, it hadn't done a big wound but it would do that he 
couldn't fly so quick, and he needed speed this time.

In spite of the pain, COndor continued leaving the place, a feet more 
and enemy's defences couldn't hit him.
